 de l&rsquo;information et des communications et l&rsquo;interconnexion mondiale offrent un grand potentiel pour acc\u00e9l\u00e9rer le progr\u00e8s humain, r\u00e9duire la fracture num\u00e9rique et d\u00e9velopper des soci\u00e9t\u00e9s de la connaissance, tout comme l&rsquo;innovation scientifique et technologique dans des domaines aussi divers que la m\u00e9decine et l&rsquo;\u00e9nergie\u00a0\u00bb (Agenda 2030 pour le d\u00e9veloppement durable de l&rsquo;ONU).<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\u00a0\u00bb1_2,1_2&Prime; use_custom_gutter=\u00a0\u00bbon\u00a0\u00bb gutter_width=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; make_equal=\u00a0\u00bbon\u00a0\u00bb _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.11.4&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment_tablet=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment_phone=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment_last_edited=\u00a0\u00bbon|desktop\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb][et_pb_column type=\u00a0\u00bb1_2&Prime; _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.10.5&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb][et_pb_blurb _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.13.0&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb body_font_size=\u00a0\u00bb16px\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin=\u00a0\u00bb|||92px|false|false\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin_tablet=\u00a0\u00bb|||0px|false|false\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin_phone=\u00a0\u00bb|||0px|false|false\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin_last_edited=\u00a0\u00bbon|desktop\u00a0\u00bb custom_padding=\u00a0\u00bb|30px||30px|false|true\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Conception<\/span><\/strong> &#8211; les technologies doivent s&rsquo;adapter \u00e0 l&rsquo;apprentissage et aux capacit\u00e9s physiques d&rsquo;un individu. Environ <a href=\"https:\/\/www.un.org\/development\/desa\/disabilities\/resources\/factsheet-on-persons-with-disabilities.html\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"2\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id-1499258446\">15 % de la population mondiale<\/span><\/a> (soit quelque <span data-token-index=\"4\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">1 milliard de personnes<\/span>) vivent avec une forme de <span data-token-index=\"6\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">handicap<\/span>. Aux \u00c9tats-Unis, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"9\" data-reactroot=\"\">les personnes handicap\u00e9es<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"10\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\"> ont <\/span><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"11\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\">moins susceptibles <\/span><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"12\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\">d&rsquo;avoir <\/span><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"13\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\">service haut d\u00e9bit \u00e0 domicile et appareils technologiques <\/span><\/a><span data-token-index=\"14\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\"> <\/span>par rapport aux personnes non handicap\u00e9es, d&rsquo;environ <span data-token-index=\"16\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">20 %<\/span>. Ils sont \u00e9galement <span data-token-index=\"18\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">moins susceptibles d&rsquo;avoir un niveau de confiance \u00e9lev\u00e9<\/span> dans <span data-token-index=\"20\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">l&rsquo;utilisation de l&rsquo;internet pour se tenir au courant des informations.<\/span> <span data-token-index=\"22\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Le contenu et les applications num\u00e9riques<\/span> doivent tenir compte <span data-token-index=\"24\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">des handicaps visuels, moteurs, auditifs, vocaux et cognitifs<\/span> afin d&rsquo;offrir un <span data-token-index=\"26\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">environnement num\u00e9rique plus inclusif.<\/span> <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\u00a0\u00bb1_2&Prime; _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.10.5&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb][et_pb_image src=\u00a0\u00bbhttps:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/visually-impaired-low-vision.jpg\u00a0\u00bb title_text=\u00a0\u00bbGuide de conception pour l&rsquo;accessibilit\u00e9 num\u00e9rique par Karwai Pun\u00a0\u00bb url=\u00a0\u00bbhttps:\/\/accessibility.blog.gov