 quelques initiatives innovantes qui s&rsquo;attaquent activement \u00e0 ce probl\u00e8me.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\u00a0\u00bb3_5,2_5&Prime; use_custom_gutter=\u00a0\u00bbon\u00a0\u00bb gutter_width=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; make_equal=\u00a0\u00bbon\u00a0\u00bb _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.11.4&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment_tablet=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment_phone=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment_last_edited=\u00a0\u00bbon|desktop\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb][et_pb_column type=\u00a0\u00bb3_5&Prime; _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.10.5&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb][et_pb_blurb title=\u00a0\u00bb1. La Puce (augmenter les comp\u00e9tences num\u00e9riques)\u00a0\u00bb _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.13.0&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb body_font_size=\u00a0\u00bb16px\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin=\u00a0\u00bb|||90px|false|false\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin_tablet=\u00a0\u00bb|||0px|false|false\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin_phone=\u00a0\u00bb|||0px|false|false\u00a0\u00bb custom_margin_last_edited=\u00a0\u00bbon|desktop\u00a0\u00bb custom_padding=\u00a0\u00bb|30px||30px|false|true\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<p>La Puce est une organisation bas\u00e9e \u00e0 Montr\u00e9al, fond\u00e9e en 1984, qui s&rsquo;est sp\u00e9cialis\u00e9e dans la fourniture de cours de formation au grand public, couvrant l&rsquo;utilisation des ordinateurs, de l&rsquo;Internet, des outils d&rsquo;applications bureautiques, des outils de collaboration en ligne et des outils de communication num\u00e9rique. L&rsquo;un de leurs programmes, <a href=\"https:\/\/lapuce.org\/programmes\/citoyens-branches\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"1\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--820905010\">\u00ab\u00a0Connected Citizens\u00a0\u00bb<\/span><\/a>, vise \u00e0 int\u00e9grer les personnes \u00e2g\u00e9es dans un monde de plus en plus num\u00e9ris\u00e9 en les associant \u00e0 des jeunes qui ma\u00eetrisent les diff\u00e9rentes technologies. En outre, l&rsquo;organisation propose un programme de formation \u00e0 l&#8217;emploi ax\u00e9 sur le d\u00e9veloppement des comp\u00e9tences num\u00e9riques aux personnes d\u00e9connect\u00e9es du march\u00e9 du travail et en cours d&rsquo;insertion professionnelle.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\u00a0\u00bb2_5&Prime; _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.10.5&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb][et_pb_image src=\u00a0\u00bbhttps:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/cropped-cropped-LAPUCE_LOGO_COULEUR_RVB-300&#215;79-1.png\u00a0\u00bb title_text=\u00a0\u00bbcropped-cropped-LAPUCE_LOGO_COULEUR_RVB-300&#215;79-1&Prime; align=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb align_tablet=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb align_phone=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb align_last_edited=\u00a0\u00bbon|desktop\u00a0\u00bb _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.11.4&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb max_width=\u00a0\u00bb75%\u00a0\u00bb max_width_tablet=\u00a0\u00bb50%\u00a0\u00bb max_width_phone=\u00a0\u00bb75%\u00a0\u00bb max_width_last_edited=\u00a0\u00bbon|desktop\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb global_colors_info=\u00a0\u00bb{}\u00a0\u00bb][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\u00a0\u00bb3_5,2_5&Prime; use_custom_gutter=\u00a0\u00bbon\u00a0\u00bb gutter_width=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; make_equal=\u00a0\u00bbon\u00a0\u00bb _builder_version=\u00a0\u00bb4.11.4&Prime; _module_preset=\u00a0\u00bbdefault\u00a0\u00bb module_alignment=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00b